HEADWORD: Leathern
<hw>Leath"ern</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Made of leather;
consisting of leather; <as>as, a <ex>leathern</ex> purse</as>.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧A <xex>leathern</xex> girdle about his loins.⟦rdquo⟧
